data.description: Welcome to a truly exceptional opportunity!  This New Daybreak home,  finished in 2023,  has so many advantages --$15K plantation shutters throughout, real shiplap from floor to ceiling on the main level fireplace, upgraded master bath with luxury tub, upstairs bedrooms both have private bathrooms,  installed storage racks in the garage--the list can go on and on.   Perfectly located in Daybreak, within walking distance of the new Watercourse, this magnificent home is a masterpiece of design, seamlessly blending farmhouse elegance with modern comforts. As you step inside, prepare to be captivated by the majestic soaring ceilings that exude an air of sophistication and warmth.   The heart of the home boasts a chef's dream kitchen, complete with a spacious quartz island suitable for any cooking adventure.  The custom range hood adds a touch of artistry to the space, with a thoughtfully positioned spigot above the gas cooktop.  Double wall ovens offer convenience, and enjoy the spacious walk-in pantry. The mudroom's clever cubbies ensure organization meets style, making daily life a breeze. Charming board and batten touches throughout the home and authentic shiplap  above the fireplace add architectural elegance to the living spaces. The master bedroom on the main level offers a tranquil retreat, with the master bathroom creating an oasis of relaxation and privacy. A true sanctuary, it features a gorgeous freestanding tub and an oversized shower.   Upstairs hosts two master bedrooms, each with its own private en-suite bathroom.  This fantastic home boasts not one, but two laundry rooms. A main-level laundry room caters to ease of living, while an additional laundry room on the upper level ensures that chores remain a breeze.  A private office space provides the perfect setting for focused work, boasting a separate outside entrance with it's own private porch.  Downstairs, spread out and relax in the great room with 9 ft. ceilings, and don't hesitate to bring over guests with three more substantial bedrooms, and two full bathrooms. Relax and feel secure that this home has all the essential systems covered.  Two tankless water heaters as well as two furnaces and a/c units ensure everyone stays comfortable. Cold storage that is vented to the outside keeps things safe, tucked away, and dry. Coveted 3-car garage and built in shelving is so convenient.   Outside, enjoy your covered porch that overlooks a park, with plenty of space to play and relax.  Daybreak has all the amenities that enhance your lifestyle. Only minutes from the new Watercourse, embark on scenic walking paths and biking trails and enjoy parks and playgrounds within minutes. Test your skills on the tennis courts, and bask in the sun at the five swimming pools available.  With every detail meticulously designed and executed, this home truly has it all. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home your own.
